[b]Questions and Answers you may or may not have:[/b]
Q) No working mr marlucia? :confused:
A) add a "/MIDI/" folder (with your midis) in the same folder as the program.

Q) No playing my mp3s mr Marluxia? :confused:
A) It's a midi player not a mp3 player
